      <div class="container">
        <p>Gather lets you quickly create an on-demand micro social network when it's time to make plans. Gather can be used to quickly see who can come tonight, or plan an entire camping trip. One simple question or 15 related ones; Gather easily scales to any complexity while staying simple.</p>

        <p>Gather isn't done when the decision is made. After everyone works together to pick the perfect restaurant, you can book it using OpenTable. Or, when the group settles on a movie, buy tickets right from Fandango. The reservations or tickets will be sent to everyone's phone.</p>

        <p>Group planning is one of those annoying things that everyone has to deal with when they want to hang out. Our goal with Gather is to mimic how you already make plans, but with the added bonuses technology can provide.</p>
