          <h2 class="meta">Phase 1: <span>Growth</span></h2>
          <p>Gather is viral. Not <em>post to your Facebook wall</em> viral &mdash; actually viral. Using it means sending it to 4-5 friends, all of whom now know about it for the next time they need to plan something.</p>
          <p>The app has a crazy-low barrier to entry. Of course it's better if the user has the app installed, however all they need is a phone that can text.</p>
